      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS bija ar\nJahsepu/ un parahdija tam Ap-\nheblofchanu/un lifke tain Scheh-\nstibu atrast/ ta Zeetuma-Sar-\nPreefscha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Zeetuma-Sargs\nve wiſſus Zeetuma-Laudis/\ns Zeetuma-Nammâ bija/Jah-\na Rohkâ/un wiſſ/ kas bij ja-\nra/to darrija wiſsch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Zeetuma-Sargs ne\nuhkoja nhs jebkuru Leetu/\nwixta Rohkâ bija/ jo tas\nNGS bija ar winnu/ un ko-\nsch ween darrija/ tain lifke\nKUNGS labbi isdohtees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Aumeisteris peedeive\nteem Jahsepu/ ka tas teem falpo-\ntu/ un tee bija kahdu Brihdi Zee-\ntunâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee redseja abbee Sap-\nni/ikfatrs fawadu Sapni/weenâ\nNakti/tas Dsehreena-Dewejs un\ntas Maisu-Zeppejs/ kas pee ta\nEgiptes Kehnika bija/ kas Zeetu-\nma-Nammâ faistiti bija/ ikkurſch\nbija fawadi ihstahstams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jahseps nahze pee teem\nRihtâ/ un apraudsija tohs/ un\nredsi/ tee bija pilni Noſkumscha-\nnas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad waizaja tas Warâis\nWirfneekus/ kas ar to Zeetumâ\nbija/fawa Kunga Nammâ/ un\nfazztja: kapehz juhfo Waigi scho-\ndeen tik skummigi raugahs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fchee fazztja us to:\nMums irr Sapnis fapnojis/ un\nfche ne irr ne weens/ kas mums\nto isstahsta. Un Jahseps atbil-\ndeja: Neggi tahs(Sapnu) Is-\nstahstichanas Deewam peederr?\nteizeet jelle man to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad isteize to Dsehreena-\nDeweju Wirfneeks Jahsepam fa-\nwu Sapni/un fazztja us to : Ran-\ngi jelte/mannâ Sapni (redseju es)\nweenu Wihna-Rohku mannâ\nPreefscha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tam Wihna-Rohkain\nbija trihs Sarri/ un tas isplau-\nke/ winna Sattums auge/ feede-\nja/ un winna Ohgas eenabzahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Warais Biktteris bija\nmannâ Rohkâ/ un es nehmu tahs\nOhgas/ un isspeedu tahs Wa-\nraus\n"
    }
  ],
